# Gemini / provider-specific LLM

- Respect the SDK and config patterns already in the repo; do not assume OpenAI shapes map 1:1 to Gemini.
- Make output structure explicit when parsers depend on it; treat model and format changes as behavior changes.
- Validate prompt + parser + consumer together when output is consumed programmatically.
